1
00:00:22,850 --> 00:00:29,850
♪Our tangled destiny
has trapped my heart in this life♪

2
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:36,060
♪Will I see you again in the next life♪

3
00:00:36,550 --> 00:00:43,500
♪Keep a piece of peach blossom
to remember the past and say goodbye♪

4
00:00:43,830 --> 00:00:49,920
♪But I still miss you
with tears in my eyes♪

5
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:57,250
♪Dig a hole, plant a tree, but the leaves
and flowers remind me of our past♪

6
00:00:57,480 --> 00:01:03,710
♪Sow the seeds of love,
but they bloom on the wrong path♪

7
00:01:04,340 --> 00:01:11,060
♪Move on, let go,
forget everything about you♪

8
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:18,220
♪Flowers fall on the road
where I fell in love with you♪

9
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,000
I've poisoned so many people.

10
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:46,240
I didn't expect my healing skills
to be as good as before.

11
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,840
Brat, it's done.

12
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:50,840
Don't rush.

13
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,160
It's not time yet.

14
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:53,000
Don't move.

15
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:00,720
Save her.

16
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,440
Auntie, are you okay?

17
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:16,880
Don't worry.

18
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:19,200
These little tricks can't hurt me.

19
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:20,880
Okay.

20
00:02:25,420 --> 00:02:30,100
=Stolen Love=

21
00:02:30,300 --> 00:02:33,140
=Episode 11=

22
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,080
Let's go.

23
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,800
Yun.

24
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:23,080
Close your eyes.

25
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,680
Don't be afraid.

26
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,120
Let's go.

27
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:36,860
(I'm gone. Don't worry.)

28
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:39,680
I know where she is.

29
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:40,920
Follow me.

30
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:55,020
(Ding Yun, Chang Shan)

31
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:02,800
Yun.

32
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:04,920
Who is she?

33
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:07,240
Do you remember Mother
used to sweep the tomb

34
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,840
of her best friend Aunt Chang?

35
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,600
Wasn't she beheaded
for poisoning the emperor?

36
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,880
I found out by chance

37
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:18,760
that someone replaced her
with a condemned prisoner

38
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,520
and imprisoned her to force her

39
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,880
to provide poison formula.

40
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,280
She refused to do it,

41
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:25,200
so they locked her in the water dungeon.

42
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:28,840
Auntie.

43
00:05:29,140 --> 00:05:30,300
(Beloved Father Chang Shan,
Beloved Mother Ding Yun)

44
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,520
Auntie!

45
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,720
Auntie!

46
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:43,920
Auntie!

47
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:47,240
My skills are as good as before,

48
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:48,640
but my body

49
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,560
is old.

50
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,360
I couldn't

51
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,360
dodge the attack.

52
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,160
Let's see a doctor.

53
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,800
Brat,

54
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:03,760
