to heal myself on purpose.

55
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,360
I didn't intend

56
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:11,160
to go back alive.

57
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:13,880
It's my fault.

58
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:17,360
I was sentenced to death,

59
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:21,840
and your mother sold everything
to see me off.

60
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,360
Before I die,

61
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:28,600
I saw my best friend's son,

62
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,800
visited my parents,

63
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:37,640
and enjoyed the view outside.

64
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,960
It's all worth it.

65
00:06:43,080 --> 00:06:43,920
No.

66
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:45,120
Auntie.

67
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:46,520
There's got to be a way.

68
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:49,760
We managed to get you out,

69
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:51,520
and we'll find a way to save you.

70
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:54,160
Stop wasting time.

71
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,000
I need to tell Yunxi

72
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,240
something important.

73
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,240
Brat,

74
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,720
leave us alone.

75
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,120
You tried

76
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:18,720
to ask me many times.

77
00:07:19,090 --> 00:07:20,360
Now

78
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:22,320
we're alone.

79
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,080
Just ask me.

80
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:29,560
Auntie.

81
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,160
Xiao Chuyi's aunt

82
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,640
is my enemy.

83
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:39,200
Do you have any evidence?

84
00:07:39,770 --> 00:07:41,480
Xiao Wan'er?

85
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,640
Yes.

86
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,840
Do you remember

87
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:49,400
Lord Zhou's maid
who died of obstructed labor?

88
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:55,840
She was the first person I killed.

89
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,520
Xiao Wan'er

90
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:01,840
threatened me with my parents' lives

91
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:03,600
to make poison

92
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:08,640
that could make her look
as if she died of obstructed labor.

93
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,960
I still remember

94
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:15,600
the baby had a crescent birthmark

95
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:20,080
on the arm.

96
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,000
Auntie,

97
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:29,280
do you know

98
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,840
how to take Lady Zhou down?

99
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,640
Come closer.

100
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,160
I'll tell you.

101
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:55,200
It turns out it was you
who asked me over.

102
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:58,240
Your Highness.

103
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:03,240
I've been waiting for this.

104
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:05,160
Your Highness, I want

105
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,680
to make a deal with you.

106
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,080
Chuyi!

107
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:30,760
I hope

108
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:33,120
I'll never be reborn

109
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:37,400
as a human.

110
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,560
Yun.

111
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:43,280
General.

112
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,800
I asked Aunt Chang to cure you

113
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:48,760
because I wanted
to repay you and Aunt Xiao

114
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,440
for saving my life.

115
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,560
He was right.

116
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:59,000
You're going back.

117
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:03,840
We're over.

118
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:05,520
General, take care.

119
00:11:08,820 --> 00:11:12,450
♪On the riverbank♪

120
00:11:12,740 --> 00:11:15,310
♪We said goodbye♪

121
00:11:15,580 --> 00:11:19,220
♪Wishing you'd come back to me♪

122
00:11:19,330 --> 00:11:22,760
♪But you never answered♪

123
00:11:23,070 --> 00:11:25,290
♪My cries♪

124
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:26,960
Lu Yunxi!

125
00:11:27,260 --> 00:11:30,650
♪Are buried in the snow♪

126
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:33,560
If you leave,

127
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:37,400
I'll cut ties with you!

128
00:11:38,820 --> 00:11:40,530
♪You left♪

129
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:42,530
♪Broke my heart♪

130
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:46,310
♪Wish you could hold me in your arms♪

131
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:49,170
♪Even your name♪

132
00:11:49,470 --> 00:11:54,580
♪Is a forbidden word♪

133
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:56,800
Let's go.

134
00:11:56,800 --> 00:11:59,720
♪I've traveled a thousand miles♪

135
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:03,690
♪Only to keep the moon in sight♪

136
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:07,460
♪For it once shone upon your face♪

137
00:12:08,290 --> 00:12:12,110
♪When you looked at me in the eye♪

138
00:12:12,110 --> 00:12:15,200
♪I've said goodbye a thousand times♪

139
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:19,170
♪Only to call your name again♪

140
00:12:19,390 --> 00:12:23,070
♪For it's the only thing♪

141
00:12:23,350 --> 00:12:27,410
